libui
------------------------------------------
Simple and portable (but not inflexible) GUI library

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.5-1
  libcairo2-1.18.4-1
  libglib2.0_0-2.86.0-1
  libgtk3_0-3.24.51-1
  libpango1.0_0-1.57.0-1
  libui-devel-4.1-1bl1
  libui0-4.1-1bl1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.45.1-1
  cmake-3.31.3-1
  cygport-0.37.3-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-13.4.0-1
  libcairo-devel-1.18.4-1
  libglib2.0-devel-2.86.0-1
  libgtk3-devel-3.24.51-1
  libpango1.0-devel-1.57.0-1
  ninja-1.13.1-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/andlabs/libui

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/andlabs/libui/archive/refs/tags/alpha4.1.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libui-4.1-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libui-4.1-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libui-4.1-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libui-4.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libui0-4.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libui-devel-4.1-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libui)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libui.README
  /usr/share/doc/libui/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/libui/NEWS.md
  /usr/share/doc/libui/README.md
  /usr/share/doc/libui/TODO.md

(libui0)
  /usr/bin/cygui-0.dll

(libui-devel)
  /usr/include/ui.h
  /usr/include/ui_unix.h
  /usr/lib/libui.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libui.pc

